{
  "stem": "4693.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I would like to mention to you one thing, because you might have-- it will be important in my life story.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was little born in Breslau because my mother went over there for confinement.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The medicine in Germany was a much higher level than it was in Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I was born seven days before the outbreak of the First World War.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And unfortunately, I was born with a so-called club foot, which was very bad, so that I couldn't walk at all.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The orthopedic surgeons in Breslau didn't know how to treat it, so they tried to treat it with a part of a different type of equipment.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was slowly turn it on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I was going every few months with my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "My mother was taking me to Breslau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I was not working until I was seven years of age.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It had a bearing on me obviously that leg and foot were a bit smaller, because it didn't develop.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And in 1921, when I was seven, we had weekend on the Baltic Sea in Sopot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "My mother decided to go to Breslau again for to get new shoes for me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And she went via Berlin during the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Or coincidentally, my mother met with a German professor of orthopathy-- Professor Gauck-- who then was the president of the German Orthopedic Society.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "When he saw me in Berlin, he told my mother she is not going anymore to Breslau, that he would take care of speaking to his colleagues about that I need an operation, and if he carries the operation out, I will be walking.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "This was of close surprise to my mother, who tried everything possible before, and couldn't get the answer to it.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
